Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,여기 연선에서...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord2.5\pos(946.667,912)}沿線
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,난도마란 놈이\N출몰하는 탓에
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,눈에 띄게\N사람 발길이 줄어버렸어
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,고용인들한테도\N쉬어달라고 해야 할 형편이야
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,요전에는 기차에서\N차장이 당해버렸다더구만
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,게다가...\N무한열차라는 놈이
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,운행 중지를\N당해버렸지 않나
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,소문으로\N듣기로는 말야...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,40명 가량...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,승객들이 홀연히\N행방불명돼버렸다고 하대
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,호오...\N흉흉하군
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,염주
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,본론으로\N들어가겠습니다만
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,그 무한열차,\N위치를 알아냈습니다
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,어느 기관고에...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,남들 눈에 띄지 않게끔\N반입되었다는 정보가...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,그런가
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,음!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs100}맛있군!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,무한열차로\N향하시겠습니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,음
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만 그 전에
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,차장의 시신이 발견되었다는\N역을 좀 보도록 하세
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,후쿠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:04:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,한숨 쉬지 말고\N단팥빵 좀 먹으렴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,응...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,손님, 오늘도 적었네
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,매일 말하고 있지만
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,어두운 시간대는\N위험하니까
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,내일 일 도울 때는\N점심부터 나오려무나
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,밤에는\N오니가 나타나거든
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,이상없음!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,둘러보고 다녔습니다만
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,문제 있어 보이는\N부분은 없군요
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,음
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,오니 같은 게 어딨어!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,또 오니 타령이야!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,안 된다구...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,열심히\N도시락 팔아야 하잖아
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,엄마는\N배도 꽤 불렀고...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,아빠는 식당 경영이\N잘 되지도 않는다는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:41.92,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,10)\fna뉴궁서m\fs40\frz29.09\c&H292A8C&\3c&H696ABF&\pos(836,610)}가정\N\N{\fs60\c&H47A4F5&\3c&H1A2F8B&}양\N식\N할\N팽\N법
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,그런 걱정은\N어른이 하면 되는 거란다
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,이른 아침이랑 밤은\N이 할미가 혼자서 할 테니까
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,할머니가 난도마한테\N습격당하면 어쩔 건데!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,너를 대신해 당하는 거라면\N바라는 바란다
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.57,0:04:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,할머니~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:58.65,Default - A,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna불꽃놀이\fs60\bord0\shad0\c&HA279F2&\pos(1268,766)\frx4\fry8\frz234.5}도\N시\N락 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:58.65,Default - A,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna편봉체\fs50\bord3\c&H7598ED&\3c&HDAEAFC&\frz212.1\frx26\fry2\pos(1606,852)}일반
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.90,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,0)\fn@a편봉체\fs45\bord4\pos(1188,352)\frz147.2\c&HAAE2FC&\3c&H52B3E1&}이십센
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.65,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,10)\fn@a편봉체\fs45\bord4\pos(1188,352)\frz147.2\c&H4D6991&\3c&H2B4C72&}이십센
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,이야, 안녕들 하신지!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,상쾌한 달밤이로군요!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,나는 오니를 찾고 있는\N몸이올신데
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,오니를 보진\N못하셨습니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,어어, 느닷없이!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,쿄쥬로 님!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,지나치게\N단도직입적이십니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,음?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,부인,\N뭔가 알고 계시는가!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,오..오니!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,이상한 소리나 하고...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐..뭔가요!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,가까이 오지 마!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,위험해!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇게 부들부들 떨다간!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,소중한 단팥빵을\N떨어뜨리고 말 거다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,오지 말라니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs90}맛있다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,오니 같은 건 몰라!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,있을 리가 없잖아!\N그런 게!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,후쿠, 그만하렴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,이 사람은...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,분명 나쁜 사람이\N아닐 게야
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,죄송합니다...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,요즘 들어 난도마 사건 때문에\N신경이 곤두서 있어서...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,방금 막\N언뜻 들은 바에 의하면
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,당신들께서는
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,어둑할 즈음부터\N준비를해서
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,우리를 위해 도시락을 팔러\N와주고 계시는군
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,실로 감사할 따름이지
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,그러한 사람들이\N상처 입는다는 일은
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,결코 있어선 안 될 일!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,안심하도록!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,난도마는\N내가 해치울 터이니!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,당신은 대체...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 이만
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,저기...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,그게...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,만일 괜찮으시다면...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,도시락 좀 사주시지\N않을래요?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,그거 좋군
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇다면...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,전부 받아가도록 하지!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,저기, 염주...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,대원들 모두에게 나눠줄\N좋은 여행 선물이 생겼군!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,여기서부터는\N나 혼자서 가지
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,수고가 많았네
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 이만
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐 하는\N사람이었던 걸까...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,도시락 사준 건\N기뻤지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,어서 돌아가자꾸나, 후쿠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,아무래도 안 좋은 느낌이\N들기 시작하는걸...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,마치 등줄기가\N얼어붙는 듯한...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,할머니?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,누...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,누구야!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna진지궁서\fs70\bord5\c&H141316&\3c&HDCE1EE&\frx16\fry354\frz321.2\move(1580,875,1194,662,0,7130)}소\N고\N기\N\N전\N골\N\N도\N시\N락
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna진지궁서\fs40\bord5\c&H141316&\3c&HD4EAFB&\frx16\fry354\frz321.2\move(2000,470,1614,252,25,7130)}고\N급
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna진지궁서\fs50\bord5\c&H141316&\3c&HDCE1EE&\frx14\fry0\frz312.6\move(930,888,534,674,0,7130)}삼\N십\N육\N센
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,나는 보시는 바와 같이\N도시락팔이라네!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,결코 수상한 사람이\N아니지!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,아니, 하지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,이 열차는\N차고에 들어갈 예정이라...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,음!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,숙지하고 있네
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,거기에 무한열차가 있다는\N소식을 들었지
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,그것에 용무가 있다!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,무한열차...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,그거라면\N이미 차고에는 없는데요?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,그런가?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘 아침 쯤에 설비가 갖춰진\N정비공장으로 옮겨졌거든요
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,저곳인데요
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,호오...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 나는\N여기서 내리도록 하지!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,에!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,내리겠다니...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:03.02,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna불꽃놀이\b0\fs40\bord0\blur5\3c&HECF7FE&\t(0,2090,\bord4\blur0\c&H2DF4F6&\3c&H32477E&)\pos(940,262)}무한
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}fan sub by kairan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,무한열차...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,과연
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,희미하지만\N오니가 있던 기척이 남아 있군
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.21,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna불꽃놀이\b0\fs60\bord5\c&H7DF4F1&\3c&H0E2845&\frx4\fry12\frz353\pos(864,707)}무한
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,어이, 당신!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,여기는\N출입금지 구역이거든?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,안녕하신가!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,나는 철도 관리국으로부터\N의뢰를 받고
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,도시락을 넣어주러 온\N인간일세
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,어이, 도시락이랜다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,야
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,대기실에서 쉬고 있는\N타츠 꼬마한테 하나 가져다줘라
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,예, 감독님
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,무한열차는 어찌 하여\N여기로 옮겨지게 된 거지?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,흥...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,차체에\N원인이 있을 리가 없건만
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,근방에서는 사람 잡아먹는 열차니\N뭐니 소문이 떠돌고 있으니
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,우리들은\N그게 분하단 말이지
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,그래서 다시 운행하기로\N결정난 지금
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,있는 힘껏 정비해서\N다시 보내주려 하고 있거든
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,다시 운행한다?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,맞아, 내일 저녁이야
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}그래서 다들 이렇게...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,오니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,오니가 있다!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,어이쿠!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,타츠 꼬마!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,물러나 있게!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,감독님...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,이 자식...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,소년을 풀어주도록!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,오니 사냥꾼인가
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,잘난 척 허세는...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,우욱...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐지, 이 냄새는!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,오니가 된 후로는\N내가 어째...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,인간의 음식은\N속이 뒤집혀서 못 참겠더군
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,내가 아는 사람들이\N정성을 담아 만든 도시락이다
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,흘려 듣지 못하겠군
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,맛없다면\N맛없는 줄 아셔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,너도 맛 없어 뵈는\N피 냄새가 나는구나, 애송이
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,맛있어 보이는 인간은\N먹어버리겠지만
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,맛없는 놈은 밤새 상처를 내며\N즐기고 있거든
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇게 된 거였나\N'난도마'
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,불쾌한 놈이로군
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,분하다면 나를...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:29.96,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)\alpha&H0&\t(20,170,\fscx200\fscy200\blur5)\c&HF8FF62&\3c&HE06016&\pos(960,940)}분하다면 나를...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,어디 베어보시든가!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,대체 뭐야!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,나를 멈출 수 있었던\N녀석은 없거든
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,내가!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,가장!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,빠르다!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,미안하구만~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,이 애송이를 안고 있으니\N베기 힘들지~?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,단숨에 죽여버리는 게\N너도 편할까?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,사...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,살려줘...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,걱정 말도록!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,자네는\N내가 반드시 구한다
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,가능할 소리를 해야지...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,어제만 해도―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,다른 여자를 질릴 때까지\N난도질해줬거든
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,과연
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,네놈의 속도는 알았다
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만\N과신은 금물이지!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,어젯밤에는 우리가 왔기에\N도망친 것인가 했더니만
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,아무래도 네놈은 감지조차\N하지 못했던 듯 보이는군
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,도망치는\N발걸음 하나는!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,확실히 빠르긴 한\N모양이구나
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐라고...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,어젯밤의 피해자도
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,우리가\N신속히 조치를 취했다
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,흉터 하나 남지 않고\N회복할 테지
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,하!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,설령 살아남았다\N치더라도
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.13,0:12:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,그년은 평생 공포에\N지배당한 채 살아가겠지~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,그리 두진 않는다!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,치유하기 어려운\N마음의 상흔도...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,우리가 오랜 시간을 들여\N보듬어 나갈 테니!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,그 정의로운 행세나 하는\N낯짝에 본때를 보여주랴?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,그 여자,\N다시 한 번 죽이러 가주지!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,그녀의 신병은 은닉했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,네놈으로선\N찾아내는 건 불가능하다
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼~\N저 도시락팔이를 노려야지
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,나랑은 상관 없는\N사람들이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,아는 사이라며~?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,그거 역 도시락이지?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,어딘지 알거든?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,꼼짝 마라!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,역시 네놈은 불쾌하군...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,나는 유쾌한데 어쩌냐~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,구하고 싶다면...\N나보다 빨리 역까지 오시든가
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,그 전에 이놈은~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,죽여두도록 하지!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,먼저 실례~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,부탁이야...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,살려줘...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,걱정 말게\N내게 맡기도록
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,그리고 내 동료도\N금방 달려올 거야
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,이쪽이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,이쪽이다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,이쪽~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,렌고쿠 님!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.15,0:14:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,의료반은?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,오고 있습니다
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,응급 처치는 끝마쳤다
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,뒷일은 부탁하지
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur3\c&HCACACA&}전집중의 호흡...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,정말이지, 후쿠는...\N말을 안 듣는 아이구나
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,돕기로 했으니까\N도울 거라구!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,안녕하세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,안녕~\N오늘도 일찍 왔구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,냄새가 나는군...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,좋았어!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,역무원분인가?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,냄새나...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,냄새가 난다!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,네년이로군?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,고약한 도시락 냄새가\N구석구석 배어 있구만
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,네년에게\N원한은 없다만...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,이것도 전부\N그 오니 사냥꾼 놈 잘못이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,도망치렴, 후쿠!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,뭔 짓거리야, 할망구...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.44,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna뉴궁서m\b0\fs35\frz5.927\pos(1206,166)\c&H150F0D&\3c&H413833&}출입금지
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,다...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,당신은...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,별고 없나?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,하..할머니!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,젠장...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,어이, 할망구...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,아까는 잘도 감히...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,대체...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,어떻게 따라잡은 거지...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,과신은 금물이라\N했을 텐데
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,어디 한 번 시험해볼까...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,내가 이 할망구의 목을\N베어 가르는 게 먼저일지
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,네놈이 내 목을 따내는 게\N먼저일지...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,시험할 것까지도 없지
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,네놈은―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,800)\pos(960,980)\fna태백산맥\fs90\c&H0ADFFF&\bord5\blur3\3c&H00FFFF&}느리다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,800)\pos(960,980)\fna태백산맥\fs90\c&H0ADFFF&\bord4\blur4\3c&H0000E5&}느리다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,화염의 호흡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,일의 형
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\pos(960,980)\fna태백산맥\c&H0AA6FF&\bord5\blur3\3c&H00F6FF&}늘어선 불빛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\pos(960,980)\fna태백산맥\c&H0AA6FF&\bord4\blur4\3c&H0000E5&}늘어선 불빛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\pos(960,980)\fna태백산맥\c&H1FC2FF&\bord2\3c&H000000&}늘어선 불빛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\fna태백산맥\fs45\c&H0AA6FF&\bord5\blur3\3c&H00F6FF&\pos(960,898)}시라누이
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\fna태백산맥\fs45\c&H0AA6FF&\bord4\blur4\3c&H0000E5&\pos(960,898)}시라누이
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\fna태백산맥\fs45\c&H1FC2FF&\bord2\3c&H000000&\pos(960,898)}시라누이
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,당신께서는...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,구해주신 거로군요...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,두 번이나...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,할머니?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,어찌 잊을 수 있을까요...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,그 존안...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,하오리...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,저와...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,후쿠의 어미는...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,20년 전, 당신 덕에\N목숨을 건졌습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:19:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,할머니,\N무슨 소리를 하는 거야?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,그것은...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,필시 제 아버지실 테죠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,저는 아버지의 뒤를 이어\N오니를 사냥하고 있습니다
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,아버지와 마찬가지로...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,당신을 지켜드릴 수 있어\N영광입니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,아직도 안 믿겨...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,죄송해요, 할머니!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,오니 같은 게\N있을 리가 없다고 해서...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,아니!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,그거면 된다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,오니를 알지 못하고
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,조우조차 하지 않은 채
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇게\N천수를 다할 수 있다면
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.71,0:19:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,그것이 제일이지!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,염주, 괜찮으십니까!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,뭘, 막 정리된 참이다
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,수고 많으셨습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,음
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,그래서, 무한열차는...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘 밤중으로\N정비를 끝마치고
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,내일부터는\N다시 운행한다고 하더군
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,그거 다행입니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,이걸로 전부\N무사히 해결된 셈이군요!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,그런 판단은\N너무 성급하군
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,40명도 넘게 잡아먹은\N오니가
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,고작 이 정도일 리가 없지
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼, 난도마는\N우리의 주의를 교란하기 위해...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,혹은 그럴지도 모르지
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.93,0:20:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,어찌 되었건 간에
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,무한열차의 오니는\N따로 있다
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,더욱 강력한...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,정체를 알 수 없는\N오니가 어딘가에 숨어 있지
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.66,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,10)\fna불꽃놀이\b0\fs40\bord0\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HE3C5F9&\t(0,320,\bord4\blur0\c&HBAD1E8&\3c&H341F41&)\pos(960,296)}무한
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇다면\N내일, 무한열차에...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,물론, 탑승한다!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,이제는\N오늘이라 해야겠다만!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,어이, 주인장\N들으셨슈?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,무한열차가\N다시 운행한다더만
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.18,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\alpha&H90&\fn@a뉴궁서m\fs40\bord5\frz290.6\c&H2D2D24&\3c&HD4D9D1&\pos(1434,702)}점검행 당했으나 이상 없음
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:52.18,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\alpha&H90&\fn@a뉴궁서m\fs40\bord5\frz290.6\c&H2D2D24&\3c&HD4D9D1&\pos(1434,702)}점검행 당했으나 이상 없음
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,헤에...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}또 이상한 일이나\N생기지 않으면 좋으련만
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,저기!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,이런!\N도시락 가게분들 아닌가
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,오늘 아침 일은\N어떻게 감사해야 좋을지...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,이거 받으시죠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,저희들로서는\N이런 것밖에 없습니다만
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.19,0:21:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,오오!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,실은 어젯밤에는\N미처 다 먹지 못해서 말이지
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,이건 무엇보다 기쁘군!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만\N요금은 치르겠네
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 아뇨!\N마음만으로도...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,그런가
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 이것은\N감사히 받기로 하고
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,거기에 있는 것들을
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,전부 사도록 하지!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs100}에에~!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,조심히 가시지요
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,근처에 오시면\N또 들러주세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,당신들에 대한 이야기는\N아버지께 반드시 전하겠습니다
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,분명 기뻐하실 테죠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 건승하시길!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,또 만납시다!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:05.41,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.38,0:22:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,뭣...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐냐, 이 생물은―?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,네, 고급 도시락\N36센 되겠습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,차나 술도 같이\N구입하심은 어떠세요?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,저돌맹진!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,하지 좀 마라!\N창피하게시리!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐 하는 걸까...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.29,0:23:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,음!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 감사히 먹도록 하지!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\fad(0,800)}맛있다!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:41.98,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.45,0:23:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,무한 열차에\N무사히 탔구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,탄지로~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,염주한테\N묻고 싶은 게 있다며?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.48,0:23:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,만나면 좋겠네!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,응!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,기둥이라고!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,나랑 승부다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.63,0:23:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,시끄러우니까\N넌 다물고 있어!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.35,0:23:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐라고, 이 자식아!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.19,0:23:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐 불만이냐!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:23:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,이제 알았으니까...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,이노스케, 진정하자!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.57,0:24:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,흥!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.74,0:24:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,바보 멧돼지가...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.62,0:24:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,그나저나, 염주라는 건\N어떤 사람일까?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.83,0:24:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,그건...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,꺾쇠 까마귀네
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.85,0:24:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,응
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.07,0:24:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,응, 응~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,꺾쇠 까마귀가 렌고쿠 씨에 대해\N알아봐준 모양이야
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.09,0:24:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 정말?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.62,0:24:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,다른 기둥분들이
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.34,0:24:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,렌고쿠 씨를\N어떻게 생각하느냐, 래!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.26,0:24:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,듣고 싶다, 듣고 싶다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.76,0:24:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,기둥!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.76,0:24:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,전부, 승부다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.10,0:24:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,예, 예~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.83,0:24:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,탄지로,\N좀 가르쳐줘 봐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.74,0:24:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,응!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.51,0:24:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼, 시노부 씨부터!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.33,0:24:46.61,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,300)\fs200\bord0\blur7\c&HFEDFED&\alpha&H60&\fscx400\fscy200\pos(1620,724)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.33,0:24:46.61,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,300)\fna진지궁서\fs50\bord6\c&H000000&\3c&HFBEEF3&\pos(1410,880)}충주·코쵸 시노부의\N\N시선에서 본\N\N{\fs65}렌고쿠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.71,0:24:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,좋은 분이시죠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.57,0:24:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,대화가 맞물리지 않을 때가\N있곤 하지만요
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.55,0:24:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,시노부 쒸~!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.56,0:24:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,좋은 냄새가\N떠올라버리네~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.10,0:24:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,다른 기둥들은~?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.44,0:24:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 단숨에 간다!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.40,0:24:53.59,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(170,10)\fna태백산맥\fs70\bord5\blur3\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(270,918)}우즈이 텐겐의\N\N경우
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.86,0:24:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,화려하다!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,나보다 눈에 띄는군~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.60,0:24:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,하지만\N엄청 좋은 놈이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.61,0:24:59.35,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,10)\fna태백산맥\fs70\bord5\blur0\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(354,190)}토키토 무이치로의\N\N{\fs90}경우
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.13,0:24:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,올빼미같아...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.19,0:24:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,쾌활한 목소리가\N편안한 느낌을 주는 사람
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.35,0:25:06.11,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(230,10)\fna태백산맥\fs70\bord8\blur0\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1596,966)}칸로지 미츠리의\N\N{\fs90}경우
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.75,0:25:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,멋진 오라버니~
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.76,0:25:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,같이 수행해서 즐거웠지!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.14,0:25:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,곧잘 귀여워 해주셨어요~
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.11,0:25:10.61,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,10)\fna태백산맥\fs70\bord8\blur0\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(458,946)}이구로 오바나이의\N\N{\fs90}경우
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.64,0:25:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,자주 이야기한다...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.53,0:25:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,성격이 좋아
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.86,0:25:10.61,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fna피오피네모\b0\fs55\bord6\c&H0E00C5&\3c&HACF4FD&\frz349.4\move(1708,984,1746,1000,23,750)}좋아
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.61,0:25:14.61,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(230,10)\fna태백산맥\fs70\bord8\blur0\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1540,912)}시나즈가와 사네미의\N\N{\fs90}경우
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.71,0:25:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,좋은 녀석이다...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.74,0:25:14.61,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fna피오피네모\b0\fs55\bord6\c&H0E00C5&\3c&HACF4FD&\frz31.39\move(236,888,192,918,0,870)}좋아
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.61,0:25:20.01,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,120)\fna태백산맥\fs70\bord8\blur0\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1168,264)}히메지마 교메이의\N\N{\fs90}　 경우
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.09,0:25:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,긍정적
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.74,0:25:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,약한 소리를\N내뱉지 않아
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.97,0:25:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,솔직함
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.14,0:25:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,어디...\N이런 느낌인가 봐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.54,0:25:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,남은 사람,\N토미오카 씨는?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.96,0:25:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,맞아, 꺾쇠 까마귀야
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.66,0:25:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,토미오카 씨는?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.81,0:25:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,응, 응
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.90,0:25:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,알았어
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.21,0:25:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,토미오카 씨는\N렌고쿠 씨에 대해서―
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.72,0:25:39.93,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(650,10)\fna태백산맥\fs70\bord5\blur0\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1624,856)}토미오카 기유의\N\N{\fs90}경우
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.05,0:25:39.93,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,10)\fna피오피네모\b0\fs55\bord6\c&H0E00C5&\3c&HACF4FD&\frz31.39\move(300,944,262,968,0,880)}좋아
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.30,0:25:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,자주 말을 걸어준다
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.20,0:25:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,..래!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.26,0:25:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,헤에~
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.24,0:25:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,염주, 모두한테\N호감을 사는 모양이구나
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.40,0:25:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,응
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.19,0:25:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,어서 만나면 좋겠다
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.92,0:25:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,염주!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.93,0:25:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,승부다~!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.25,0:25:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,이노스케...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.23,0:25:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,렌고쿠 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.05,0:25:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,다음화!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.88,0:26:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,귀멸의 칼날 무한열차편\N제2화
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.30,0:26:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,「깊은 잠」!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.61,0:26:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,다들, 함께 승차하자꾸나!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.90,0:26:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-형님~!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.62,0:26:08.88,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(230,10)\fna태백산맥\fs90\c&H0AA6FF&\bord5\blur3\3c&H4A93FF&\fscx300\fscy300\t(0,230,\fscx100\fscy100)\pos(1000,904)}계속
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.62,0:26:08.88,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(230,10)\fna태백산맥\fs90\c&H0AA6FF&\bord4\blur4\3c&H0043FF&\fscx300\fscy300\t(0,230,\fscx100\fscy100)\pos(1000,904)}계속
